    {
      "id": "edge-contract-root",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "🔗 Edge Contract (Normative)",
      "position": {
        "x": 102,
        "y": 16
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 280,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Edge Contract\n\n**Authority:** Normative\n\nEvery edge created, mutated, rendered, or interpreted by humans, agents, or tools **MUST** conform to this contract.\n\nEdges express relationships.\n\nPlain edges remain valid without classes. Edge classes are the canonical semantic upgrade path.\n\nThis graph is the contract.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
