    {
      "id": "edge-optional",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "2. Optional Fields",
      "position": {
        "x": 140,
        "y": 360
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Optional Fields\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"string\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"edgeClassRef\": \"/library/classes/edges/task-depends-on.edge-class.node\",\n    \"edgeClassKey\": \"task.depends-on\",\n    \"edgeClassMeaning\": \"target must happen before source can complete\"\n  },\n  \"style\": {},\n  \"state\": {},\n  \"sourcePort\": \"port-id\",\n  \"targetPort\": \"port-id\"\n}\n```\n\n- `label` is human-readable only\n- `data` holds semantic attributes and optional edge-class assignment metadata\n- `style` and `state` are metadata\n- ports may be omitted; omitted ports are treated as `root`",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
