    {
      "id": "edge-validation",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "6. Validation Rules",
      "position": {
        "x": 360,
        "y": 760
      },
      "width": 480,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Validation Rules (REQUIRED)\n\nValidators MUST enforce:\n\n1. `id`, `source`, and `target` exist\n2. source and target exist\n3. if `type` exists, it is a string\n4. provided ports satisfy node port contracts\n5. omitted ports are interpreted as `root`\n6. if `edgeClassRef` exists, the referenced edge-class artifact exists\n7. if both `edgeClassRef` and `edgeClassKey` exist, they agree\n8. manifest allows mutation\n\nFailure blocks persistence.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
