    {
      "id": "edge-agent-rules",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "8. Agent Rules",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 1160
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Agent Rules (REQUIRED)\n\nAgents MUST:\n- read edge + port contracts\n- refuse incompatible edges\n- prefer add/remove over rewire\n- emit errors, never guess\n- preserve edge identity",
