    {
      "id": "edge-portability",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "9. Portability Guarantee",
      "position": {
        "x": 600,
        "y": 1160
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Portability Guarantee\n\nEdges remain valid when:\n- ports are omitted\n- styles are ignored\n- editors differ\n- renderers change\n- class defaults are unavailable and only instance data remains\n\nMeaning must survive transport.\n\nWhere possible, carry both `edgeClassRef` and `edgeClassKey` so transport can preserve both durable authority and lightweight local discoverability.",
